If you need to clone object then what are the options
1. constructor - will have to know all the parameters from object to clone and one by one copy it to a 
contructor call or builder. So would have to know internals of an object necessarily. and What if some
parameters are private. would not be able to access them.

When you want to clone objects and dont want to know internals of object we receive a PRototype type of object.
This interface necessitates to implement clone method. So the responsibility of cloning is given to 
object itself. and user of Prototype 
